ZH: 今天的严寒天气让我不想出门。
EN: The severe cold weather today makes me not want to go outside.

ZH: 穿上厚厚的羽绒服才能应对这种严寒。
EN: I have to wear a thick down jacket to cope with such severe cold.

ZH: 在严寒的冬天里，人们躲在家中享受温暖。
EN: In the freezing winter, people stay at home to enjoy the warmth.

ZH: 长时间暴露在严寒中可能导致冻伤。
EN: Extended exposure to extreme cold can cause frostbite.

ZH: 这个地区的严寒气候使得植物难以生存。
EN: The harsh cold climate in this region makes it difficult for plants to survive.

ZH: 她在严寒的天气中仍然坚持每天晨跑。
EN: She still insists on jogging every morning in the severe cold weather.

ZH: 他们为了在严寒的冬天里保暖而点燃了壁炉。
EN: They lit the fireplace to keep warm during the freezing winter.

ZH: 这个小屋里没有暖气，夜晚的严寒很难忍受。
EN: Without heating in this cabin, the nighttime severe cold is difficult to bear.

ZH: 此时露天露营将会受到严寒的影响。
EN: Camping outdoors at this time will be affected by the severe cold.

ZH: 在正午时分严寒的气温让人感到惊讶。
EN: The severe cold temperature at noon is surprising.

ZH: 由于严寒，我们取消了登山活动。
EN: Due to the extreme cold, we canceled the mountaineering activity.

ZH: 在严寒的天气中，热茶是最好的取暖方式之一。
EN: Hot tea is one of the best ways to keep warm in severe cold weather.

ZH: 这片区域因为严寒而有大量积雪。
EN: This area has a lot of snow due to the severe cold.

ZH: 家里没有供暖设施，只能依靠厚厚的被子抵御严寒。
EN: There is no heating in the house, so we can only rely on thick blankets to withstand the severe cold.

ZH: 预报显示未来一周将会有严寒的天气。
EN: The forecast shows that there will be severe cold weather in the next week.

ZH: 在这个严寒的季节，家里的火炉是宝贵的财产。
EN: In this harsh cold season, the fireplace at home is a valuable asset.

ZH: 北方地区的严寒气候对动植物的生存带来了挑战。
EN: The severe cold climate in the northern regions poses challenges for the survival of animals and plants.

ZH: 我们已经习惯了每年冬天的严寒。
EN: We have become accustomed to the severe cold every winter.

ZH: 在严寒的冬天，街上的人很少见。
EN: In severe cold winters, there are few people on the streets.

ZH: 穿上保暖的衣物，我们可以抵御严寒。
EN: We can resist the severe cold by wearing warm clothes.
